12
00:00:37,093 --> 00:00:39,019
Hả?

13
00:00:39,077 --> 00:00:41,040
Tên cậu là gì?

14
00:00:41,040 --> 00:00:42,077
Là người không xem TV?

15
00:00:43,027 --> 00:00:44,098
Tateishi Yousuke.

16
00:00:44,098 --> 00:00:46,061
Cậu không nhận ra tôi sao?

17
00:00:47,024 --> 00:00:47,094
Eh?

18
00:00:48,095 --> 00:00:51,057
Tôi là Tachibana Misaki.

19
00:00:52,032 --> 00:00:53,074
Misaki...

20
00:00:57,020 --> 00:00:59,021
